\p
\v 1 In e nhag r…®p Yesu Kristo\f + \fr 1:1 \ft  N…ôgkiarien Gris ramni ‚ÄúMesaea.‚Äù N…®pran ramni m…ô ‚ÄúYermam…ô yame Kughen r…®m…®rpen m…ô tukrher-p…ô k…®n.‚Äù\f* m…®n…ô, k…®rik e King Deved, k…®ni k…®rik m…®n e Ebraham.\x - \xo 1:1 \xt Jen 22:18; 1 Kron 17:11\x*   
\li1
\v 2 M…ôr…®g r…®p Yesu yame r…ôkup…ôn, Ebraham. K…®ni Ebraham in r…®m Aesak, k…®ni Aesak in r…®m Jekob, k…®ni Jekob in r…®m Juda m…®ne naorahini m…®n…ô,\f + \fr 1:2 \ft Juda m…®ne naorahini m…®n…ô iri…ô m-fam twelef, kamni k…®mi…ô kw…ôn…ôr…ôus twelef kape Isrel.\f*   
