\v 11 k…®ni Josaea in r…®m Jehoeakin m…®ne piauni m…®n…ô, k…®ni kwas…®g ik…®n, n…ôm…ô Babilonia k…®mnhav…ôn apa Isrel, mhav…ôh-si ta n…ôm…ô Isrel tuk tan…ô atuatuk kap…ôri…ô, mhap…®k …ôri…ô mhav…ôn apa Babilonia.\x - \xo 1:11 \xt 2 King 22-24; 2 Kron 36:10; Jer 27:20\x*   
\p
\v 12 K…®ni in e nhag r…®p Yesu m…®n…ô, r…®rikakun ye n…®p…®g yame kw…ôn…ôr…ôus m…®n…ô kape Isrel k…®mn…®sar…ô Babilonia.  
