\v 18 In e n…ôvsaoyen k…®n narhayen kape Yesu Kristo. N…®s…®n Yesu, nhag…®n e Meri. K…®m…®rpen-ta m…ô tukr…ôri-p…ôn kw…ôn k…®rik, nhag…®n e Josef. M…ôr…®g k…®r…®p…ôh han…ô n…®war…ô-kwisien, k…®ni Josef r…®p…ôh nap…®r-p…ônien tukun, m…ôr…®g Nanm…®n kape Kughen r…®mnor Meri ror t…®p…®n. K…®ni narmam…ô kw…ôs…ôm m…ô Meri r…®nor t…®p…®n.\x - \xo 1:18 \xt Luk 1:27,35\x*  
\v 19 K…®ni kafan yerman Josef r…®m…ô tukr…ôp…ôh in, m…ôr…®g in yem…ô atuatuk, [m…®p…ôh norkeikeiyen m…ô tukror Meri raur…®s ye n…®mr…® narmam…ô], r…®kin ram…ôs…®k m…ô tukr…ôp…ôh ap…®s-ap…®s …ôm…ô Meri.  
