\q2 K…®ni m…®r…ôh t…®ni k…®rik yerman,  
\q1 K…®ni tukhen-p…ôn nhag…®n k…®m…ô Emanuel.‚Äù\rq (Aes 7:14)\rq*  
\p (N…®pran e ramni m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúKughen ramar…ô k…®taw…ô min.‚Äù)   
\p
\v 24 Josef r…®mn…ôm-ta n…ômr…ôrhavyen a, k…®ni m…ôri-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien yame agelo kape Kughen Yermaru r…®m…®ni, k…®ni m…®v…ôn, m…®k…®r Meri r…ômhen k…®n kafan piraov…®n, m…®rav…ôn iman yerkwanu.  
