\p
\v 12 K…®ni kwas…®g ik…®n, k…®m…®s…ômr…ôrhav m…®s…ôm Kughen ramor kwir…®g k…®mi …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTakhap…ôh nharer…®g-p…ônien tuk King Herod, mhakurao-p…ôn ye swatuk p…®s…®n, mharer…®g-p…ôn im…ômi…ô ik…®n.‚Äù   
\s1 Josef m…®ne Meri k…®r…ôr…ôh Yesu m…®wap m…®rhuv…ôn apa Ijip  
\p
\v 13 K…®ni kw…ônhat…ôrhav-ta, m…ôkneik…®n Josef r…®mnamr…ôrhav m…ôm agelo k…®rik kape Kughen Yermaru r…®mat…ôrhav-p…ô tukun m…®m…ô, ‚Äú!∆érer aihuaa! M…®r…ôh kwajikov…ô e iriu n…®s…®ni m…®rhap m…®rhuv…®n apa Ijip. K…®ni m…®rhar…ô aik…®n m…®rheriaji Yo …ôm…ô jakni-pre tuk ik m…ô takrher…®g-p…ô m…®n. Meinai p…ôh nien m…ô tuk tu, King Herod tukru…ô marha k…®n kwajikov…ô e m…ô tukrhopni.‚Äù   
\p
\v 14 Ror p…ôn, yenp…®g, Josef rarar, m…®r…ôh kwajikov…ô iris…®r n…®s…®ni m…®rhap m…®rhuv…®n Ijip.  
