\q1
\v 18 ‚ÄúNarmam…ô ipak…ô tuk Betlehem\f + \fr 2:18 \ft  Gris ramni ‚ÄúN…ôm…ô Rama.‚Äù Rama in taon k…®rik ipak…ô tuk Betlehem.\f* k…®m…®s…ôr…®g piraov…®n k…®rik ramas…ôk p…®k,  
