\q1 Piraov…®n a in Rejel\f + \fr 2:18 \ft Rejel e n…®s…®n kw…ôn a Isrel kupan; kamni k…®m…ô Rejel in mama kape n…ôm…ô Isrel. N…®p…®g ramni ‚ÄúPiraov…®n a in Rejel tukras…ôk‚Äù n…®pran ramni m…ô n…®pian Isrel m…®n…ô fam tuksas…ôk.\f*. In ramas…ôk tuk kafan kwajikov…ô m…®n…ô.  
\q2 R…®p…ôh n…®p…ôhyen m…ô narmam…ô tuks…ôgkiar huv…ô k…®min, meinai kafan kwajikov…ô narman m…®n…ô kw…ônhamh…ô fam.‚Äù\rq (Jer 31:15)\rq*   
\s1 Josef m…®ne Meri m…®ne kwajikov…ô krh…®t…ôrhav Ijip m…®rher…®g-p…ôn Nasaret  
