\v 27 K…®ni n…®p…®g tukm…ô n…ôhig r…®p, k…®ni yapiw…ôn raiyu, k…®ni n…®m…ôtag ramuh nim…ô, r…ôus…ôrku, mowhan …ôp…®r-p…®r.‚Äù   
