\v 10 Yesu r…®mn…ôr…®g n…ôgkiarien e, rakur p…®k k…®n. K…®ni marar m…®ni-p…ôn tuk narmam…ô khapsaah yam…ô m…®ne khakwas…®g k…®n In m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúYakamni …ôfrak…®s tuk …ômi…ô m…ô, nar apnap…®g kw…ôn e p…ôh nien m…ô yem…ô Isrel, m…ôr…®g yakp…ôh n…ôm-han…ôyen yem…ô Isrel k…®rik yame kafan nhat…ôt…ôyen rehu…ô r…ômhen k…®n in.  
