\v 2 Nhag aposol\f + \fr 10:2 \ft Aposol, n…®pran ramni m…ô ‚Äúyermam…ô kher-p…ôn k…®n.‚Äù Yesu r…®m…®rpen narmam…ô twelef kafan m…ô tukrher-p…ôn k…®n …ôri…ô kamhav…ôn masor wok kape Kughen.\f* twelef kape Yesu m…®n…ô, iri…ô e: yame ram…ôkupan, Saemon, nhag…®n k…®rik e Pita; m…®ne naorahini Andru; m…®ne Jemes m…®ne Jon, ji Sebedi mir;  
