\v 24 M…ôr…®g bot ravir…ô ta ye nu, m…®r…ôhp…®k…®n n…®m…ôtag. Peao-peao ramuh bot. \fig Khavhir…ô ye bot mas…ôm n…®p…®g …ôut…ôn|alt="Boat in a storm" src="HK074C.jpg" size="span" loc="Top of page" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="MAT 14:24" \fig*   
