\v 11 Nar ram…ôm…®r iru…ô, tukm…ô r…®v…ôn yerki yermam…ô, to r…®p…ôh norien r…ômk…®m…®k ye n…®mr…® Kughen. Nar ramt…ôrhav ye n…ôkwai yermam…ô ramor n…ômk…®m…®k ye n…®mr…® Kughen.‚Äù\x - \xo 15:11 \xt Mat 12:34\x*   
