\v 5 ‚ÄúYermam…ô yame rav…ôh nhag…®k, mamasitu k…®n ye kwajikov…ô k…®rik r…ômhen k…®n yame, nasituyen e in e tukror m…®n k…®mi Yo.\x - \xo 18:5 \xt Mat 10:40; Luk 10:16; Jon 13:20\x*  
\v 6 M…ôr…®g Kughen tukror narp…®nien ehu…ô k…®mi narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kamhavi-p…ôn kwajikov…ô yam…ô m…®ne k…®shat…ôt…ô irak, m…ô tuksor t…ôvhag…ô has. K…®ni narp…®nien a tukr…®skai rapita yame tukruk-p…ôn kapier k…®rik ye n…®p…ôt…ôk nuan, karkw-…ôrhav-p…ôn k…®n apa ye tame tahik m…ô tukr…ômn…®m.\x - \xo 18:6 \xt Mak 9:42; Luk 17:1-2\x*   
