\v 17 K…®ni tukm…ô r…®p…ôh n…ôr…®gien …ômi…ô, hani-…ôrhav k…®mi nim…ôhuak. K…®ni tukm…ô r…®p…ôh n…ôr…®gien nim…ôhuak, s…ôm in r…ômhen k…®n yem…ô iru…ô, u…ô [yem…ô has r…ômhen k…®n] yermam…ô yame ram…ôrer tuk mane kape takis.   
