\v 28 ‚ÄúM…ôr…®g n…®p…®g yorwok a r…®mav…ôn, m…ôm yermam…ô k…®rik yame r…®mnor kaon k…®min r…ômhen k…®n wan handred taosen vatu …ôm…ô.\f + \fr 18:28 \ft  N…ôgkiarien kape Gris ramni m…ô ‚Äúwan handred denari.‚Äù\f* Iriu kwis yorwok mir kape king. K…®ni yorwok yame king r…®mn…ôru-k…®n kafan kaon, rarar m…®rapt…ôr…ôk…®n yermam…ô yame ramor kaon k…®min, m…®r…ôh n…®p…ôt…ôk nuan, m…ôv…®t, mamni m…®m…ô, ‚Äò!Arp…®n kafam kaon yame n…®mnor k…®mi yo!‚Äô   
