\v 35 Yesu r…®m…®ni-ta nuhp…®k…®nien a, m…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô k…®mi…ô nakhap…ôh n…®s…ôru-k…®nien norien has yame piaumi…ô m…®n…ô kasor ir…ômi…ô, R…®m…®k apa ye rao ye neai tukr…®v…ôhsi-pre m…®n narp…®nien r…ômhen k…®n yame king a r…®mnor k…®mi kafan yorwok.‚Äù\x - \xo 18:35 \xt Mat 6:15; Mak 11:25; Efes 4:32; Kol 3:13\x*   
\c 19  
