\p K…®ni k…®nas…ôsiw…ôn-…ôsiw…ôn k…®mi …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚Äú?Tukshaw ni e? Tukm…ô k…®taw…ô khani m…ô, ‚ÄòKughen r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn nehu…ôyen k…®mi Jon,‚Äô m…ôr…®g Yesu tukr…®m…ô, ‚Äò?Tukm…ô Kughen r…®m…®v…ôhsi-p…ôn nehu…ôyen k…®min, rhawor e k…®mi…ô nakhap…ôh nhaniyen n…ôfrak…®sien iran?‚Äô  
