\p K…®ni Yesu r…®ni-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúRatuatuk. K…®ni yakamni-pre …ôfrak…®s tuk …ômi…ô m…ô n…ôm…ô has r…ômhen k…®n narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôrer tuk mane kape takis, m…®ne n…®piraov…®n kape swatuk k…®mnhau…ô ye narmaruyen kape Kughen kwas…®g ik…®n k…®mi…ô.  
