\r (Mak 12:1-12; Luk 20:9-19)  
\p
\v 33 K…®ni Yesu r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúK…®ni s…ôr…®g m…®n ru nuhp…®k…®nien k…®rik. Yermam…ô k…®rik r…®mn…ôsim k…®n kafan plantesen k…®n grep, markopar…®n-p…ôn. K…®ni m…®k…®r kw…ôt…ôgtap k…®rik kape n…ôvi…ôs…®s-p…ônien kw…ônkwai grep iran. M…ô nehen tukraiyu, k…®v…ôh kor waen k…®n. K…®ni in mor nim…ô apomh k…®rik m…ô tukram…ôrer ik…®n mamarha huv…ô tuk kafan plantesen. K…®ni in m…ôr…ôhu plantesen ai ye kwerm…® narmam…ô t…®ks…®n, tukhap…®k n…ôri…ô t…®ks…®n, mhav…ôh-si-p…ôn nan k…®rik r…ômhen k…®n n…ôrokien. Mar…ô, m…®t…ôrhav m…®n aik…®n m…®v…ôn ye tan…ô p…®s…®n.\x - \xo 21:33 \xt Aes 5:1-2 \x* \fig Nim…ô apomh kape narha-huv…ôyen tuk plantesen kape grep|alt="Vineyard watchtower" src="HK076A.jpg" size="span" loc="top of page" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="MAT 21:33" \fig*  
