\v 42 K…®ni Yesu r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúTukm…ô ror k…®mi…ô nakhap…ôh n…®s…ôvhek…®n-han…ô-yen n…ôgkiarien yame N…ôkw…ôkw…ô kape Kughen r…®m…®ni m…®m…ô,  
