\v 3 Ror p…ôn, takas…ôkeikei m…®s…ôri-p…ôn, m…®sor nar…®mnar fam yame kamhani-pre tuk …ômi…ô. M…ôr…®g norien kap…ômi…ô tukr…®p…ôh n…ômhenien k…®n norien kap…ôri…ô. Meinai iri…ô khap…ôh n…®sorien naha nhag…®n yame iri…ô kamhani.\x - \xo 23:3 \xt Mal 2:7-8\x*  
\v 4 Iri…ô kas…ôkeikei k…®mi narmam…ô mham…ô tuks…ôri-p…ôn loa yame in r…ômhen k…®n kajip…ô pam, m…ôr…®g to khap…ôh nhav…ôhsi-p…ônien kwerm…®ri…ô m…ô tuksasitu ir…ôri…ô.   
