\v 31 K…®ni m…®sarh iakei fam iran, mhar…ôhsi-ta m…®n kot …ôwhao mhav…ôhsi-p…ôn kafan neip…ôn. Mhak…®r mhat…ôrhav, mhav…ôn m…ô tukharuk hakt…ô ye nai kamarkwao k…®n.   
