\v 35 K…®ni k…®mnharuk hakt…ô In ye nai kamarkwao k…®n. K…®ni m…®s…ôwhai kafan neip…ôn mas…ôuk…®r tukun, m…ô tukm…ô yame rapita, k…®ni in rav…ôh kafan. Nar e r…®t…ôrhav-p…ô mor n…ôgkiarien kupan kape profet ruau…ô m…®nor n…ôfrak…®sien k…®n yame ramni m…ô,  
\q1 ‚ÄúK…®m…®s…ôwhai neip…ôn kafak m…®saruk…®n daes tukun.‚Äù\f + \fr 27:35 \ft  N…ôgkiarien e r…®k…ôk ye kopi akwas t…®ks…®n kape Niutesteman. Keinein m…ô Matiu atuk r…®m…®rai, u…ô yermam…ô k…®rik r…®mn…ôs…ôk-…ôpnis ye n…ôgkiarien kape Matiu.\f*\rq (Sam 22:18)\rq*   
\p
\v 36 K…®ni m…®s…ôkw…ôt…ô aik…®n masarha tukun.  
\v 37 K…®ni k…®rai-p…ôn n…ôgkiarien k…®rik ye nai k…®rik ramni m…ô k…®m…®s…ôm-p…ôn nar has k…®rik iran m…®m…ô, ‚ÄúIn e Yesu, King kape n…ôm…ô Isrel.‚Äù K…®ni k…®sarkw…ôt…ôr…ôk…®n-p…ôn a kap…ôn kap…ô ik…®n yerp…®r…®g.  
\v 38 K…®ni mhar…ôh yem…ôkr…ôh mir k…®raru, mharuk hakt…ô m…®n …ôriu iris…®r Yesu. K…®rik ye matuk, k…®rik ye mawor.\x - \xo 27:38 \xt Aes 53:12\x*  
\v 39 K…®ni narmam…ô yam…ô m…®ne kas…ôriw…ôk ye swatuk k…®sarha-p…ôn m…®s…ôm, k…®sarh iakei iran. Kas…ôwhan-…ôwhan kap…ôri…ô kap…ô,\x - \xo 27:39 \xt Sam 22:7; 109:25\x*  
\v 40 mham…ô, ‚Äú!Eh! !Ik yermam…ô kape natm…ôt…ôg-…ôt…ôgien Nim…ô Ehu…ô kape Kughen m…®ne nor-m…®nien ye n…®p…®g k…®sis…ôr …ôm…ô!\x - \xo 27:40 \xt Mat 26:61; Jon 2:19\x* ∆óntah. Tukm…ô Ik Ji Kughen …ôfrah, eiwaiyu-ru ye nai kamarkwao k…®n m…®v…ôh m…®ragh atuk Ik.‚Äù   
\p
\v 41 K…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, jif pris m…®n…ô m…®ne n…ômhajoun m…®n…ô kape loa kasarh iakei m…®n iran.  
\v 42 Mamhani-p…ôn tuk …ôri…ô m…®n…ô mham…ô, ‚ÄúIn r…®v…ôh m…®ragh ta narmam…ô khapsaah. M…ôr…®g r…®p…ôh n…ômhenien tuk n…®v…ôh-m…®ragh-atuk-ien In. Rhuv…ô m…ô king kape n…ôm…ô Isrel tukreiwaiyu ye nai kamarkwao k…®n p…ôh k…®s…ôm, k…®ni mhani n…ôfrak…®sien iran.  
\v 43 In rhat…ôt…ô ye Kughen. Tukm…ô Kughen rorkeikei, p…ôh r…®v…ôh-si ta In. Meinai In ramni m…ô In Ji Kughen.‚Äù  
\v 44 K…®ni ye norien k…®rikian…ô …ôm…ô m…®n, yem…ôkr…ôh mir yame k…®m…®ruk hakt…ô …ôris…®r Yesu kawarpakw…ô k…®min.   
\s1 Yesu r…®mamh…ô  
