\v 58 R…®v…ôn m…ôm Paelat, k…®ni maiyoh-p…ôn m…ô tukreighaan k…®n n…®prai Yesu. K…®ni Paelat r…®m…ô tukr…®r…ôhsi-p…ôn n…®prai Yesu k…®min.\x - \xo 27:58 \xt Dut 21:22-23\x*  
\v 59 K…®ni Josef r…®v…ôn m…®r…ôh n…®prai Yesu, muvr…®g k…®n neip…ôn haw…ôn k…®rik nhag…®n e linen.  
\v 60 K…®ni m…®r…ôh m…®v…ôn m…ôr…ôhu-p…ôn ye n…ôpag kapier k…®rik yame k…®m…®k…®r wi …ôm…ô k…®m…ô kafan. K…®ni m…ôp…ôr-p…ôr p…ôn k…®n kapier ehu…ô k…®rik m…ôtap…®g k…®n n…ôpag kapier. K…®ni in mamv…ôn.\x - \xo 27:60 \xt Aes 53:9\x*  
\v 61 Ye n…®p…®g a, Meri, pian Magdala, m…®ne n…®fnagni, iriu kaokw…ôt…ô ipak…ô tuk n…ôpag kapier.   
