\v 63 Mham…ô, ‚ÄúYemehu…ô. R…®kimaw…ô ram…ôs…®k m…ô n…®p…®g kw…ôn a, yermam…ô kape neiku…ôyen r…®mnamragh han…ô, m…®m…ô, ‚ÄòN…®p…®g k…®sis…ôr tukru…ô m…®v…ôn, jak…®mragh m…®n ye n…®mh…ôyen kafak.‚Äô\x - \xo 27:63 \xt Mat 12:40; 16:21; Mak 9:31; 10:33-34; Luk 9:22; 18:31-33; Jon 2:19-21\x*  
\v 64 Ror p…ôn, yaksaiyoh ik m…ô takher-p…ôn k…®n kafam t…®ks…®n mobael tukhav…ôn masarha tuk n…ôpag kapier m…®seriaji-p…ôn n…®p…®g k…®sis…ôr ruau…ô m…®v…ôn ta. Tam…ô, kafan narmam…ô m…®n…ô khau…ô m…®s…ôkr…ôh k…®n n…®pran, mhani-…ôrhav mham…ô ru…®mragh m…®n ye n…®mh…ôyen kafan. Neiku…ôyen a tukrahas p…®k rapita fam nhajounien eiku…ô yame Yesu r…®namor.‚Äù   
\p
\v 65 K…®ni Paelat r…®m…ô, ‚ÄúHak…®r mobael m…®n…ô, mhav…ôn m…®sor naha nhag…®n yame nakharkun m…ô taksor m…®sarha huv…ô tuk n…ôpag kapier.‚Äù  
\v 66 K…®ni khav…ôn m…®sor, masarha huv…ô tuk n…ôpag kapier. M…®sor mak k…®n nehe kandel ye kapier m…ô tukm…ô k…ôsu…ô ta k…®n kapier, nehe kandel tukrakap…®r, k…®ni m…®s…ôtu mobael m…®n…ô tukun.   
